This paper focuses on investigating the effects of random seed on model performance and robustness, which are key concerns in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
